Rather then be affected by the hallucination, Cyanide actually laughed the 
twisted bot not fearing pain or the pit itself. He concentrated hard and soon 
the hallucination dissapeared and he smiled.

Cyanide; "When youve fought an Infecticon hand to hand you tend to lose all 
emotion and feeling of pain.."

Cyanide laughed as he was about to send an acid blast at halucigen but 
Skywarp decided to do that by sending a large amount of laser blasts from the 
scorpions double laser gattling guns at the bot sending 35 blasts at the 
close range bot in all.
